snippet.title: Gungrave G.O.R.E - Exclusive Cinematic Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Watch this cinematic gameplay trailer for Gungrave G.O.R.E, the new gory indie action game releasing this fall!

Gungrave Gore has three words it wants you to remember: bullets, beauty, and blood. In this upcoming indie action game, you'll dance through a ballet of death as you splatter your enemies into a fine red paste. Coming to PS4, PS5, Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X, and PC in Fall 2022.

#IGN #IGNSummerofGaming
